## Run the following command to install Rider

```shell
ansible-playbook -vvv main.yml -i "localhost" --connection="localhost" --extra-vars "state=present" -t="rider" -K
```

Optional variables:

```shell
ansible-playbook -vvv main.yml -i "localhost" --connection="localhost" --extra-vars "state=present rider_plugins=['com.github.copilot']" -t="rider" -K
```

The Rider role resolves plugin installation to the current user when available and falls back to `ubuntu` by default. Override with `rider_plugin_user` if needed.